{"type": "article", "id": 25824, "title": "灵活的家具组合", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-22T07:12:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120302weD2GYQh847oKVx6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套可以自由组合的家具系统名为罗弗敦（lofoten），是<a href=\"http://nichettostudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Luca Nichetto</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.casamania.it/\" target=\"_blank\">casamania</a> 所设计的产品，灵感源于挪威的同名群岛。这套各自独立、又能通过组合成为具有统一的视觉语言的家具系统包含了：装有软垫的座椅和靠背、桌子以及其他家具配件。它最大的特点就是高灵活度，适用于各种大小的空间，视使用情况的不同可以随时调整，充满了动手的趣味和可能性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120300aUEs9wJCrTubqfmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59535452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120300Tb5VdC0x2Ji4oazn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120301EVuGnBlOhXMqo5gZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120301sMGiLOxDNz6joka4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n"}